A versatile essential oil, Tea Tree Essential Oil is a powerful ingredient that helps you keep your hair, nails and body healthy 

✨ HAIR 
Mix a few drops of tea tree oil into regular shampoo and wash your hair as normal.  

✨ ACNE TREATMENT 
Add 4 drops of tea tree oil to a half cup of water. Apply to the face with a cotton pad once daily. 

✨ NAIL CARE 
Add two drops of tea tree oil into coconut oil or water and apply it to your nail and cuticle. 

✨ AROMATHERAPY 
Apply the essential oil on your sheets before sleeping or simply dab the oil on cotton balls and keep it in the room to rejuvenate your senses.
